The paper focuses on the application of Linked Data, which is a subfield of databases and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely category. The paper also discusses query languages and optimisation, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL). The use of process calculus and operational semantics is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
